Question: Many universities require that freshman live on campus dorm during the first year of college. In your opinion, is this a good or a bad thing? Explain your opinion on this issue.
Answer:
Its a good thing. usually students go to college in another city away from hometown. its often their first time to leave their family. They need to stay in the crowd. some of them are shy, so its important to force them to live with others and get along. Also, its usually safer to live on campus.